descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][color=#00ff00][size=4]BIOGRAPHY
[/size][/color]
[size=3]Larissa was a princess from a distant land that was tired of the routine she carried. Her dream was to travel the world and dive into countless adventures, but the king was not happy about it because he believed it would be too dangerous for her. Despite Larissa be very skilled in combat, since she received the best training that money can provide, the King was not yet convinced that she was prepared to be a real warrior. One day, the kingdom was attacked by marauders and the King ended up being kidnapped. Larissa awakened her hidden power and thus managed to save him, proving to everyone what she was capable. The King was convinced that Larissa was prepared for her long journey through the hostile lands of Tamriel and gave her the opportunity to create her own story. It was later revealed that she was also a dragonborn.[/size]
